name: Worthless 2021
description: 6400 x 2750 Pixels, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe Photoshop, 2008 (Remastered 2021), I created this Zero Dollar Bill in 2008 as a reaction to the global financial crisis, the politics of money and central banking. Corporations and large financial institutions are bailed out and citizens are left holding the bag. Once again this artwork is relevant with the massive printing of the US Dollar. instagram.com/brianromero / twitter.com/brianromero / brianromero.com
